ed="T" n="0852b12"/><persName key="A012976">釋宗合</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000017135">閩越</placeName>人也，遊<placeName key="PL000000028928">嶽</placeName>泛<placeName key="PL000000028611">湘</placeName>，以求知識焉。<lb
ed="T" n="0852b13"/>其為僧也，介立而寡慾，群居終日，唯笑而已。<lb
ed="T" n="0852b14"/><placeName key="PL000000000126">南楚</placeName>之人且多信重。後居<placeName key="PL000000028639">延壽院</placeName>，故諫議大<lb
ed="T" n="0852b15"/>夫<persName key="A012979">賈<roleName>公</roleName>玼</persName>判軍府<ptr target="#n2842"/>，聞之，往謁見，言話不接。<lb
ed="T" n="0852b16"/>輿人<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1858"/>議曰「得道之人，豈入恒量<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1857"/>度中耶？」<persName key="A012979">賈</persName>乃<lb
ed="T" n="0852b17"/>堅請往<placeName>文殊院</placeName><ptr target="#n2843"/>住持。爾日登座，聊舉禪要<lb
ed="T" n="0852b18"/>而散。明日，告眾曰：「有故暫出，諸賢不宜留<lb
ed="T" n="0852b19"/>難。」其裝束若行脚狀，渡<placeName key="PL000000020128">彭䗍</placeName>，至<placeName key="PL000000027963">黃州</placeName>驛前，<lb
ed="T" n="0852b20"/>屹然立終。遐邇奔競觀<anchor xml:id="beg0852sgsz3"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0852sgsz3"/>。時馬鋪使臣為營<lb
ed="T" n="0852b21"/>喪務，造塔於立終處，則<date from-iso="+0969-01-26" key="j20750062075389" to-iso="+0970-02-13"><name>開寶</name>二年</date>也，今號<placeName key="PL000000059392">真<lb
ed="T" n="0852b22"/>身院</placeName>是歟。又<placeName key="PL000000025048"><placeName>澠池</placeName><placeName>大安寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A013003">釋道因</persName>，不知何<lb
ed="T" n="0852b23"/>許人也。遊處<placeName key="PL000000025054">澠池</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000023537">瀍</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000059393">㵎</placeName>之間，自言：「出家人<lb
ed="T" n="0852b24"/>守儉，則少<anchor xml:id="beg0852sgsz5"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>于</sic><corr>干</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0852sgsz5"/>人。與畜類為同行，則無是<lb
ed="T" n="0852b25"/>非盈耳。」甞養一烏犬，出入起臥，不相忘捨。<lb
ed="T" n="0852b26"/>每食以鐵鉢就火而炊，<anchor xml:id="beg0852003"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>麋</sic><corr>糜</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0852003"/>熟，與犬同食。<lb
ed="T" n="0852b27"/>或前或後，行止奇異，人莫能測。一旦僧亡，犬<lb
ed="T" n="0852b28"/>亦坐斃。今<placeName key="PL000000025048">大安寺</placeName>塑其像，而肉身兩存，<date notBefore-iso="+0968-02-07" key="j20746522077920" notAfter-iso="+0977-01-18"><name>開寶</name></date><lb
ed="T" n="0852b29"/>中也。<placeName key="PL000000023602">洛下</placeName>崇信，香<anchor xml:id="beg0852sgsz7"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0852sgsz7"/>滿龕焉。</p>
